thread.title: Kylie Jenner jealous’ of Kendall Jenner’s modelling career
thread.title_full: Kylie Jenner jealous’ of Kendall Jenner’s modelling career

author: Wires English | Press Trust of India
title: Kylie Jenner jealous’ of Kendall Jenner’s modelling career
text:
Comments 
Los Angeles, Oct 12: Supermodel Kendall Jenner has revealed that there was a time when her sister Kylie was annoyed about her older sister’s growing fame.Kendall, 19, shares a very close bond with her 18-year-old sister but she admits when her catwalk career took off, it initially “bothered” Kylie, reported People magazine. (Also Read: Kylie Jenner and boyfriend Tyga rarely fight) 
“She’s a Leo so she loves attention, and at certain points when we were younger, it bothered her that I was getting attention in terms of my modelling,” Jenner said.”I think that’s a natural younger-sister thing to be jealous. I was jealous of her at times too!” But now with careers of their own, the sibling duo are supportive as ever. 
“Now she loves what I do and supports me. She’s very into fashion and always texts me when I’m doing a big show like ‘That is the sickest thing ever! How were the clothes?’ It’s as much a part of her as it is mine.”Kendall went on to add that her sister is a bit of a ‘wild card’ specifically when they were growing up.”When she was little, she was always crazy, chatty, and all over the place. My brother would get a new girlfriend, and she would lock her out of the house in the rain just because she thought it was funny. She’s a wild card.”
